  "title": "Environmental Control Officer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Monitor site environmental control and compliance with regulations</li><li>Conduct regular site inspections on environmental issues</li><li>Identify environmental risks and recommend mitigation measures</li><li>Ensure proper waste management, dust control and noise control on site</li><li>Maintain environmental records, reports and documentation</li><li>Liaise with site teams, consultants and authorities on environmental matter\t</li><li>Support implementation of environmental management plans</li><li>Communicate effectively with internal teams and subcontractors</li><li>Able to work independently in a fast-paced construction environment</li><li>Relevant site/environment experience preferred</li></ul>",
